English (Convenience Translation)
======================================================================

The Japanese text above is authoritative. This English translation
is provided for convenience only.

All data in this repository (scenario text, locale files, etc.)
is copyrighted material belonging to circle "mochimochiyama"
(the "Rights Holder").

■ Game Information
Title: Usamimi Dougu-ya-san to Osawari Dekasegi Boukensha Seikatsu
Circle: mochimochiyama
Purchase: https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/work/=/product_id/RJ01575130.html

■ Permitted
- Creating translation mods using this data (any translation method)
- Free distribution of translation mods
- Publishing gameplay videos, streams, and screenshots with translation mods applied

■ Prohibited
- Commercial use of this data or translation mods (including paid distribution)
- Redistribution of original text outside the context of a translation mod
- Distribution including game images, audio, program code, or other non-text assets
- Creating content that substitutes the game experience using this data
- Any action that infringes upon the rights of third parties

■ Attribution
When distributing a translation mod, include the following in the
mod description or README:
- Game: Usamimi Dougu-ya-san to Osawari Dekasegi Boukensha Seikatsu
- Circle: mochimochiyama
- Purchase: https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/work/=/product_id/RJ01575130.html

■ Rights
All copyrights to the data in this repository belong to the Rights Holder.
These guidelines constitute a limited license for creating translation mods
and do not imply any transfer of copyright or other rights.
The Rights Holder reserves the right to modify or revoke these guidelines.

■ Disclaimer
This data is provided "as is." The Rights Holder assumes no liability
for any damages arising from the use of this data.

■ Treatment of Translation Works
This section applies between contributors who submit translation works
to this repository (hereinafter "Translators") and the Rights Holder.

1. Copyright
Translators retain copyright of their translation works.

2. License Grant to the Rights Holder
By submitting a Pull Request to this repository or sending translation
works to the Rights Holder, the Translator grants the Rights Holder a
non-exclusive, irrevocable, royalty-free, perpetual license to use the
translation works for the following purposes:
  - Incorporation into the Work and its revisions or additional content
  - Paid distribution of the Work with such translations incorporated
  - Redistribution of the translation works as translation mods via
    this repository
This license is limited to the Work. Use in sequels, ports, or other
derivative works requires separate consent from the Translator.

3. Attribution Obligation
When incorporating or distributing translation works, the Rights Holder
shall credit the Translator (by name, handle, or anonymous designation
per the Translator's preference) in the in-game credits screen and on
the DLsite product page.

4. Independent Distribution by Translators
Translators may independently distribute their own translation works
within the scope of these guidelines.

5. Translator Representations and Warranties
Translators represent and warrant that their translations do not
violate any applicable laws and do not infringe upon the rights of
third parties. The Rights Holder reserves the right to refuse
incorporation or distribution of translations deemed inappropriate.

6. Limitation on Revocation
While the Rights Holder reserves the right to modify or revoke these
guidelines as a whole, the license granted in Section 2 above for
translation works already submitted shall not be revocable.
